      "situation": "a broadcaster, streaming platform, or OTT service wants to acquire distribution rights for a catalogue or individual title, requiring negotiation and execution of a distribution agreement",
      "motivation": "maximise distribution revenue and audience reach while protecting content value and contractual terms",
      "outcome": "distribution agreement executed, content delivered to distributor, first payment schedule activated",
      "success_criteria": [
